pageProduct.name: Thompson's Prostate Manager 90 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's Prostate Support is a nutritional and herbal complex supporting normal male physiology and function

Thompson's Prostate Support supports prostate health. A formulation blend of antioxidants, vitamins, minerals and Nettle Root to:
- Reduce free radicals formed in the body.
- Support urinary health in men.
- Support reproductive system health.

Product Claims: No added gluten, lactose, nuts, shellfish, dairy, egg, fish, sesame seeds. No artificial flavours.

Size: 90 Capsules

Warnings

Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. This product contains Selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150mcg for adults of Selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. Contains zinc which may be dangerous if taken in large amounts or for a long period. Contains: sulfites and trace amounts of pollen. If symptoms persist, seek the advice of a healthcare professional.

CAUTION

Keep out of reach of children. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Conifer phytosterol complex 185.71mg
equiv. Sitosterol 130mg
Colecalciferol 25mcg
equiv. Vitamin D3 1000 IU
Zinc Gluconate equiv. Zinc 15mg
Selenomethionine 372.6mcg
equiv. Selenium 150mcg
Lycopene 15mg
Urtica Dioica (Nettle) Ext. 18.75mg
derived from dry root 300mg

Contains: Contains zinc. Contains sulfites and trace amounts of pollen.

Directions

Adults - Take on capsule daily (with food), or as professionally prescribed.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a dry place.

Storage Temperature: Below 25°C.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Remove cap and recycle glass.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
